title: Reba McEntire - Love Revival (2008)
description:
2007 was certainly a big year for MCA Nashville recording artist Reba McEntire. She released the clever and almost brilliant Reba Duets. The kick off the new year Hallmark chose McEntire to be their Valentine Artist for 2008. Following in the footsteps of Martina McBride and others.

In this collection, Reba has selected some of her tracks of love, and added 4 news songs for the cause. Interestingly enough you receive 2 Reba Hits on this album, mixed with several smaller charting songs and filler tracks. Love Revival was never released as a single by Label MCA Nashville.
